var app=new Vue({el:"#app",data:{backgroundColor:"white",message:"To-Do",todos:[{text:"Learn JavaScript"},{text:"Learn Vue"},{text:"Build something awesome"}]},template:'<div class=\'container\'>\n    <h1> {{message}}</h1>\n    <div class="form-container">\n      <input id=\'input\' type=\'text\' required>\n      <button @click="addItem">Add Item</button>\n      <button @click="removeList">Clear List</button>\n    </div>\n    <ol id=\'itemList\'>\n      <li v-for=\'(todo, index) in todos\'\n        :key="index">\n        <input id="cb" @click="removeItem(index)" type="checkbox">\n        <span :style="textEdit" contentEditable="true">\n          {{todo.text}}\n        </span>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>',methods:{addItem(){let e=document.getElementById("input");e.value.length>0&&app.todos.push({text:e.value,done:!1}),e.value=""},removeItem(e){app.todos.splice(e,1),document.getElementById("cb").checked=!1},removeList(){let e=document.querySelector("#itemList");for(;e.childNodes;)e.removeChild(e.childNodes[0])}},computed:{textEdit(){return{backgroundColor:this.backgroundColor}}}});